#: ../../source/language/java/sink.rst:67
msgid "主流JSON库"
msgstr "Mainstream JSON Libraries"

#: ../../source/language/java/sink.rst:68
msgid "主流的JSON库有Gson、Jackson、Fastjson等，因为JSON常在反序列化中使用，所以相关库都有较大的影响。"
msgstr "Mainstream JSON libraries include Gson, Jackson, and Fastjson. Because JSON is often used in deserialization, related libraries can have a broad impact."

#: ../../source/language/java/sink.rst:70
msgid "其中Gson默认只能反序列化基本类型，如果是复杂类型，需要程序员实现反序列化机制，相对比较安全。"
msgstr "By default, Gson can only deserialize primitive types. For complex types, developers need to implement the deserialization mechanism themselves, which makes it relatively safer."

#: ../../source/language/java/sink.rst:72
msgid "Jackson除非指明@jsonAutoDetect，Jackson不会反序列化非public属性。在防御时，可以不使用enableDefaultTyping方法。相关CVE有CVE-2017-7525、CVE-2017-15095。"
msgstr "Unless @jsonAutoDetect is specified, Jackson does not deserialize non-public properties. For defense, avoid using the enableDefaultTyping method. Related CVEs include CVE-2017-7525 and CVE-2017-15095."

#: ../../source/language/java/sink.rst:74
msgid ""
"FastJson是阿里巴巴的开源JSON解析库，支持将Java Bean序列化为JSON字符串，也支持从JSON字符串反序列化到Java "
"Bean，相关CVE有CVE-2017-18349等。"
msgstr ""
"FastJson is Alibaba's open source JSON parsing library. It supports "
"serializing Java Bean objects into JSON strings and deserializing JSON "
"strings into Java Bean objects. Related CVEs include CVE-2017-18349."

